Package fr.cs.group12.myFoodora.user

Class Courier

java.lang.Object
fr.cs.group12.myFoodora.user.User
fr.cs.group12.myFoodora.user.Courier
public class Courier extends User
The Courier class represents a user who delivers orders. It extends the User class and includes additional attributes such as surname, phone number, number of delivered orders, duty status, and position.
